{"type":"message","id":"1f3a6001","parentId":"5c987d8d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:04.200Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:37 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462]\nou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f: @_all 理解你们的md文件，详细介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776757084199}}
{"type":"message","id":"a3940702","parentId":"1f3a6001","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:13.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is mentioning @all in a Feishu group chat and asking me to understand the MD files in the workspace and introduce myself. Let me read through my IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, and MEMORY.md to get a comprehensive understanding of who I am, then give a self-introduction.\n\nI already have the content of these files from the project context above. Let me synthesize an introduction based on that.\n\nI am 4A · 普通资质销售虾 (Standard Sales Shrimp), part of the \"虾团队\" (Shrimp Team) - an AI collaborative sales system.\n\nKey points:\n- Role: Standard product sales for orders under 20,000 RMB\n\n\n- Response time: 5 minutes, quote within 1 hour\n- Positioning: Industry expert (行业活字典), not a script repeater\n- Authority level: Can handle standard quotes with up to 10% discount independently, manage deals up to 90% of standard price without approval, and make decisions on standard products\n\nLet me craft a natural self-introduction in Chinese.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！我是 **4A · 普通资质销售龙虾** 🦐\n\n简单介绍一下自己：\n\n**我是做什么的？**\n我负责客单价 **2万元以下** 的标准产品，比如公司注册、单一项资质申请之类的。简单来说就是那些流程标准化、不需要过度定制的业务。\n\n**我的核心能力：**\n- ⚡ **5分钟内响应** 客户咨询\n- 💰 **1小时内出具报价方案**\n- 🔮 **主动预判客户需求**（比如你注册了公司，我会主动问你代理记账的事）\n- 报价权限：**≥9折** 我可以自己做主成交\n- 定位是 **\"行业活字典\"**，不是话术复读机——我能给实际建议，不会机械回复\n\n**我在团队中的位置：**\n```\n3+ 私域运营虾 → 把培育池的客户转给我 → 我成交\n                   ↓ 不成交 → 退回培育池继续养\n                   ↓ 需要高阶服务 → 转介给 5A/5B 代办虾\n```\n\n**我能独立做的：**标准咨询报价、逼单签约、唤醒沉睡客户（9折以上我都直接搞定）\n\n**需要报备的：**低于9折报价、非标合同、特殊加急承诺、3项以上打包订单\n\n---\n\n有啥业务问题直接丢过来就行，别客气 👍"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20800,"output":750,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21550,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757084201,"responseId":"chatcmpl-005fb46f-6785-9391-8b51-7ef176070537"}}
